    "ClickHouse server is ready and accepting connections",
    "ClickHouse configuration applied:",
    "  Hardware-detected settings (CPU cores: 16, RAM: 123.8GB)",
    "  max_threads: 16",
    "  max_memory_usage: 30.0GB",
    "  max_bytes_before_external_sort: 10.0GB",
    "  max_bytes_before_external_group_by: 10.0GB",
